```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant V as Validator<br/>(Python)
    participant VN as Validator Node<br/>(Node.js)
    participant MN as Miner Node<br/>(Node.js)
    participant M as Miner<br/>(Python)
    participant Apify as Apify API
    participant Gravity as Gravity API<br/>(Macrocosmos)

    Note over V,VN: 1. Create Synthetic Task
    V->>VN: GET /create-synthetic-task
    VN->>Apify: Search for places/keywords
    Apify-->>VN: Return search results
    VN-->>V: {typeId, metadata, timeout}

    Note over V,M: 2. Query Miners
    V->>M: GenericSynapse(type_id, metadata, timeout)
    M->>MN: POST /fetch<br/>{typeId, metadata, timeout}
    
    alt Google Maps Reviews
        MN->>Apify: runActorAndGetResults<br/>(placeFIDs, maxItems, language, sort)
        Apify-->>MN: Review items array
    else X Tweets
        MN->>Gravity: POST OnDemandData<br/>(source, keywords, limit, keyword_mode)
        Gravity-->>MN: Tweet items array
    end
    
    MN-->>M: {status, responses, timestamp}
    M-->>V: GenericSynapse with responses filled

    Note over V,VN: 3. Score Responses
    V->>VN: POST /score-responses<br/>{typeId, metadata, responses, responseTimes}
    VN->>VN: Calculate scores<br/>(quality, speed, volume)
    VN-->>V: {scores, statistics, detailedResults}
